"its a total number that will be shown in the Query Count dynamic tag, "
"Listings Grid still will show number of items set in the <b>Show/Per Page "
"Limit</b> option. To count all possible results count, but show only N items "
"in the grid - leave this option empty and set N into <b>Show/Per Page Limit</"
"b> option"
msgstr ""
